---
title: Southeast Asian Chicken & Noodles with Crispy Shallots Pre-Prepped | Three Steps | Ready in 15
description: With pre-chopped, pre-marinated ingredients, our new Fresh & Fast recipes are on the table in just 15 minutes. Perfect for busy weeknights - and busy people. This week, tuck into a lightly spiced chicken noodle stir-fry packed with flavour and garnished with coriander and peanuts for an added crunch.

*Heads-up - you'll need a microwave for this recipe.*
